f77ff5cbde305c3433f561438d0f36af329b","tid":2032440,"uid":82752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72f17624776ec359216082deb48bc79b9589e43c","tid":2032440,"uid":54334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"Tg換相？<br />\n有種射多啲 射到成個港島都係煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57662ef03a69cf167fe11fcd80cdee92af298348","tid":2032440,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"推到繼續上國際頭條<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=89e5c642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"8ba04e772f49d23856ad644346b9f1eb5af58136","tid":2032440,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91619a29b2fa369ed4703a7d055ee1b70386dcb4","tid":2032440,"uid":62192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"Sogo感謝際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"社會主義鐵拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50aee0af080ba24f43d55080c8fa71290afe43e","tid":2032440,"uid":272271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"附近有無撐惡安街站，大量人群向個邊徹捉佢哋一齊食TG"}]}